Package: mica
Title: Matrix Imputation with Correlation-Aware Diagnostics
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("MICA Authors", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "mica.pkg@proton.me")
Description: Tools for completing partial meta-analytic correlation matrices.
    Provides a deterministic positive-definite fill (mica()) and a Bayesian
    Stan engine (mica(..., engine = "stan")) with per-cell diagnostics,
    triage labels, and posterior uncertainty intervals for missing cells.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
